metadata.name: Unicorn #3676
metadata.description:
All of us have dreams, and everyone would like to meet a fairy, a genie, a wizard, or someone else who will make our dreams come true in a snap of a finger or with the wave of a wand. But we're the only ones who can do it. We are those magical unicorns, unique, inimitable, with our own qualities and magical abilities.
These unicorns are the visualization of our inner selves that makes our dreams come true. An embodiment of all the best with a huge positive magical power.

Twitter: @unicorn_nft_art
Web: https://unicorn-nft.web.app/

by @lucky26puch, @AgataBaranova17

Life is full of them.

Observe them.
Be present.
Be curious.
Be aware.

metadata.name: Raumstreicher for Ukraine #8
metadata.description:
"I paint energy, not the soul." Ukranian artist Kazimir Malevich, 1924

100% of primary and secondary sales are donated to `Save the children` (https://thegivingblock.com/donate/save-the-children/) one week after publication, supporting victims of the war against Ukraine.

Raumstreicher divides space in boxes, randomly.

# Shortcuts
* 's' | export png image
* 'c' | center the artwork
* 'r' | reset the perspective
* scrolling | zoom in and zoom out 
* left-clicking + dragging | rotate the camera
* right-clicking + dragging | pan the camera position

100% generative
created with p5.js
